```plantuml
@startuml icoxfog417_karura
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Kintone Environment" as Kintone {
  rectangle "Karura Master App" as MasterApp
  rectangle "Karura Client Plugin" as ClientPlugin
}

rectangle "Karura Server" as Server #lightsteelblue {
  rectangle "REST API" as API
  rectangle "Model Building Pipeline" as ModelPipeline
}

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> Kintone

' Kintone interactions
User --> MasterApp : Configure ML task
User --> ClientPlugin : Start training / Get predictions

' Karura Server interactions
MasterApp --> API : Send training / prediction requests
ClientPlugin --> API : Send training / prediction requests

' Model Building Pipeline interactions
API --> ModelPipeline : /train
API --> ModelPipeline : /predict
ModelPipeline --> API : Return predictions/results

' Data and Model Management
ModelPipeline --> ModelPipeline : Data extraction from Kintone\nFeature engineering\nModel selection and training
ModelPipeline --> ModelPipeline : Model evaluation\nModel persistence

@enduml
```